Package org.intermine.biovalidator.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Parser<T>
    Base interface for Parsers, user of this interface can simple call to parseNext(), in order to get next parsed data to be validated.
    ValidationResult
    This interface represents the result of a validation, instance of this will be returned on calling validate method any Validator
    Validator
    A common interface for all validators, any validator will an implementation of this interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultValidationResult
    A simple and default implementation of ValidationResult
    DefaultValidationResultStrategy
    A default implementation of ValidationResultStrategy
    ErrorMessage
    Represents an immutable error message
    Message
    Represents an immutable Message that can be created by validator whenever validator finds an invalid data.
    ValidatorBuilder
    Builder class to instantiate a Validator with customization
    ValidatorHelper
    Provides helper methods create validator.
    WarningMessage
    Represents an immutable warning message
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ParsingException  
    ValidationFailureException
